  "flags": {},
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 9th level, you gain the ability to summon a rushing jet of water from the elemental plane of water and direct it against your foes. As a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Standard-Actions\">standard action</a>, you can create a jet of water in a 60-foot line that deals 1d6 points of damage per two sorcerer levels you possess, and blinds the target that was struck for 1d6 rounds. A&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Reflex\">Reflex</a>&nbsp;save (DC 10 + 1/2 your sorcerer level + your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Charisma-Cha-\">Charisma</a>&nbsp;bonus) reduces the damage by half and negates the blinding effect.</p>"
    },
